{"prompt": "Generate a website for a edtech platform. The website should be cozy and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Cozy EdTech</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #FFF5E0; /* A warm, light beige */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #E96E6E; /* Brand red */\n            color: #FFF5E0; /* Light beige text for contrast */\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -50px;\n            left: -50px;\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 200px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 245, 224, 0.3); /* Lighter shade of beige for a subtle glow */\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 960px;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        .section {\n            background-color: #FFFFFF;\n            padding: 40px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .section:nth-child(even) {\n            flex-direction: row-reverse;\n        }\n        .section-text {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n        .section-text h2 {\n            color: #E96E6E; /* Brand red */\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .section-image {\n            flex-shrink: 0;\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 200px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            background-color: #E96E6E; /* Brand red for placeholder image */\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: #FFF5E0;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #E96E6E; /* Brand red */\n            color: #FFF5E0;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #C05A5A; /* Darker shade of red */\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: #E96E6E; /* Brand red */\n            color: #FFF5E0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .section {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                text-align: center;\n            }\n            .section:nth-child(even) {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            .section-image {\n                width: 150px;\n                height: 150px;\n                margin-top: 20px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Learn with Comfort</h1>\n        <p>Discover a cozy and engaging way to expand your knowledge. Personalized learning, tailored for you.</p>\n        <a href=\"#courses\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Courses</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n            <div class=\"section-text\">\n                <h2>Your Cozy Learning Space</h2>\n                <p>We believe learning should be a joy, not a chore. Our platform is designed with comfort and engagement in mind, creating a warm environment where you can thrive. Imagine a comfy armchair and a warm cup of tea \u2013 that\u2019s the feeling we want you to have while learning.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"section-image\">\n                <p>Warm <br> Atmosphere</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"courses\" class=\"section\">\n            <div class=\"section-text\">\n                <h2>Engaging Courses</h2>\n                <p>From beginner basics to advanced topics, our courses are crafted by experts to be both informative and delightful. Interactive lessons, supportive community, and flexible pacing make learning a pleasure.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"section-image\">\n                <p>Diverse <br> Subjects</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"community\" class=\"section\">\n            <div class=\"section-text\">\n                <h2>Connect & Grow</h2>\n                <p>Join a community of like-minded learners. Share insights, ask questions, and celebrate your progress together. Our forums and study groups are here to support your journey.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"section-image\">\n                <p>Supportive <br> Community</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Cozy EdTech. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}